            </div>

            <div class="w-[10em] text-[16px] text-center  py-[0.5em] px-[0.8em] flex flex-col justify-center items-center ">
              <p class="whitespace-nowrap">Shopify Development</p>
              <p class="text-[13px] leading-[20px]">conversion rate optimization analysis.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-[10em] text-[16px] text-center py-[0.8em] border-l border-white ">
